messages.messageBody:
Hi Purple cowboy boot lovers,
I'm way behind but had to say- I have purple cowboy boots. I don't want to part with them though. Got them at Salvation Army on 1/2 price day and still paid $9 for them. They're worn and I really do need them for riding, but the color's kind of a joke around here. They work great though.
Mary T.
